          "page_code": "",
          "page_id": 0,
          "descrip": "<h2><strong></strong></h2><h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 1.444; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Play, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300;\">Sale Price: $</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Play, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: line-through;\">369.99</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Play, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: inherit;\">Clearance Price:&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">$295.99</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.444; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: Play, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">All sales are final for clearance items.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">We do our best to show in the pictures any blemishes, scratches or dents, all blemishes are purely aesthetic and do not affects the performance or reliability of the part. Due to inventory variances, pictures may not reflect the actual blemishes and should be referred to as examples.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p></h2>\r\n\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <div id=\"product-description\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;\">\r\n        <div style=\"padding: 20px;\">\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">Product Overview</h2>\r\n            <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">The Sinister Diesel Cold Side Charge Pipe is a performance upgrade for the 2017-2024 Ford 6.7L Powerstroke Diesel Engine. Designed to replace the factory plastic cold side intercooler pipe, which is prone to cracking and leaking under high boost conditions. Crafted from high-grade aluminum tubing, this charge pipe can endure high temperatures and pressures, ensuring your engine operates at peak performance. This product does not require any tuning. The Sinister Diesel Cold Side charge pipe is a perfect replacement for Fords OEM Part numbers HC3Z-6F073-A and HC3Z-6F073-B.</p>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">Features</h2>\r\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px;\">\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">6061 Aluminum Alloy Construction</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">CNC Mandrel Precision 3\" Tubing for Perfect Fit</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">5-Ply Silicone Boots Rated to 400 PSI</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Stainless Steel Spring Boot Clamps for a Reliable Seal</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Powder Coated and Polished in Sinister Blue</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Higher Flow and Lower Turbulence Airflow for Increased Power</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">2 Year Warranty</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Made in the USA</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">50 State Legal. Carb EO# D-721-8 Valid for 2017-2019 Ford F250/F350 6.7L Powerstroke</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">Benefits</h2>\r\n            <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">Our Cold Side Charge Pipe is designed to boost airflow to your engine, reducing turbo lag and increasing power and torque. The mandrel-bent tubing with smooth transitions minimizes turbulence and pressure drops, leading to improved throttle response and quicker spool-up times.</p>\r\n            <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">High quality materials mean this charge pipe is built to last. Our boots are rated to withstand up to 400 PSI, while the stainless clamps ensure a secure and leak-free fit. The powder-coated finish not only enhances durability but also adds a sleek, polished look to your engine bay. Enjoy the peace of mind knowing you won't be left stranded on the side of the road like the Factory Cold Side Charge Pipe will.</p>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">Easy Installation</h2>\r\n            <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">The Sinister Diesel Cold Side Charge Pipe includes all necessary hardware and silicone couplers, making installation quick and straightforward. Upgrade your 2017-2024 6.7L Ford Powerstroke with this high-performance charge pipe and enjoy enhanced performance and reliability.</p>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">Kit Includes:</h2>\r\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px;\">\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">(1) Cold Side Charge Pipe</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">(2) Silicone Boots</li>\r\n                <li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">(4) Stainless Steel Spring Clamps</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <h2 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; color: #000;\">FAQs</h2>\r\n            <div style=\"background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-top: 20px;\">\r\n                <h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #007bff;\">How difficult is the installation process?</h3>\r\n                <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">Installation is straightforward, with all necessary hardware and silicone couplers included for a secure and leak-free fit. Basic mechanical skills and tools are required.</p>\r\n                <br>\r\n                <h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #007bff;\">Is this charge pipe a replacement?</h3>\r\n                <p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 20px 0;\">Yes, this part is a direct replacement part for Ford part numbers HC3Z-6F073-a and HC3Z-6F073-B</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color: #fff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><strong>CARB LEGAL VALID FOR 2017-2019 TRUCKS</strong><br><strong>CARB EO# D-721-8</strong></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>",
